" class=\"reviewer-name\">puzzlout<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 22, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">It is a good and easy to use plugin.\nIf you enable to prevent browsing to \"wp-admin\", the 404 page is displayed.\n\nHowever, when you changed the login page from \"wp-login\" to \"mynewlogin\", anyone can find the new connection page.\nI'll submit the bug to the author.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">\u041e\u0442\u043b\u0438\u0447\u043d\u044b\u0439 \u043f\u043b\u0430\u0433\u0438\u043d<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tsipan\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/479596011726a734d7dac6ef76059598?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/479596011726a734d7dac6ef76059598?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tsipan\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tsipan<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 29, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">\u041e\u0447\u0435\u043d\u044c \u043e\u0431\u043b\u0435\u0433\u0447\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0436\u0438\u0437\u043d\u044c!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">\u0442\u0430\u043a \u0441\u0435\u0431\u0435<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/seven74\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/129e241f807ee6bc4d62508352872b4a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/129e241f807ee6bc4d62508352872b4a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/seven74\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">seven74<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 21, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">\u041f\u043b\u0430\u0433\u0438\u043d \u0438\u0437\u043c\u0435\u043d\u044f\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0441\u0435 \u0430\u0442\u0440\u0438\u0431\u0443\u0442\u044b \u0438 \u0442\u0430\u043a\u0438\u043c \u043e\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0437\u043e\u043c \u0434\u0435\u043b\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u043d\u0435\u0432\u043e\u0437\u043c\u043e\u0436\u043d\u044b\u043c \u0440\u0430\u0431\u043e\u0442\u0443 \u0444\u0438\u043b\u044c\u0442\u0440\u043e\u0432 \u043d\u0430 \u0441\u0430\u0439\u0442\u0435.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
